$head Bug$$
Selecting this $xref/FrameLink/Bug/link/$$ should do nothing.
In the XHTML version with Firefox 1.5 and only using $code name$$ attributes,
it opened a new window.
OMhelp now uses both the $code name$$ and $code id$$ attributes
and this link functions properly.


